<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Seller Registration - Canadian Bazaar Admin</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e74c3c;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8;
        }
        .seller-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .seller-details h3 {
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 150px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .detail-value {
            flex: 1;
            color: #333;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #c0392b;
        }
        .button.approve {
            background-color: #28a745;
        }
        .button.approve:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }
        .button.reject {
            background-color: #dc3545;
        }
        .button.reject:hover {
            background-color: #c82333;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .status-pending {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
        }
        .status-verified {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
        }
        .priority-high {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
            color: #721c24;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Canadian Bazaar Admin</div>
            <h1>New Seller Registration</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="alert-box">
            <strong>üîî New Registration Alert:</strong> A new seller has registered and requires your approval.
        </div>

        <div class="priority-high">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Action Required:</strong> Please review the seller details below and approve or reject their registration.
        </div>

        <div class="seller-details">
            <h3>üìã Seller Information</h3>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Company Name:</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><strong><%= companyName %></strong></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Email:</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= email %></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Phone:</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= phone %></div>
            </div>
            
            <% if (businessNumber) { %>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Business Number:</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= businessNumber %></div>
            </div>
            <% } %>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Registration Date:</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= registrationDate %></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Registration Time:</div>
                <div class="detail-value"><%= registrationTime %></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Status:</div>
                <div class="detail-value">
                    <span class="status-badge status-pending">Pending Approval</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">Verification:</div>
                <div class="detail-value">
                    <span class="status-badge status-pending">Not Verified</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <strong>üìù Next Steps:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Review the seller's information for completeness</li>
                <li>Verify business credentials if provided</li>
                <li>Check for any red flags or suspicious information</li>
                <li>Approve or reject the registration</li>
                <li>Contact the seller if additional information is needed</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
            <h3>üéØ Quick Actions</h3>
            <p>Click the buttons below to take action on this registration:</p>
            
            <a href="<%= adminDashboardUrl %>" class="button approve">‚úÖ Review in Admin Panel</a>
            <a href="<%= approveUrl %>" class="button approve">‚úÖ Approve Registration</a>
            <a href="<%= rejectUrl %>" class="button reject">‚ùå Reject Registration</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <strong>üîç Additional Information:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Seller ID:</strong> <%= sellerId %></li>
                <li><strong>Registration IP:</strong> <%= registrationIp %></li>
                <li><strong>User Agent:</strong> <%= userAgent %></li>
                <% if (referralSource) { %>
                <li><strong>Referral Source:</strong> <%= referralSource %></li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Note:</strong> This is an automated notification from the Canadian Bazaar seller registration system. Please review the seller's information and take appropriate action.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated notification from Canadian Bazaar Admin Panel.</p>
            <p>For support, contact the development team or check the admin dashboard.</p>
            <p>¬© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Canadian Bazaar. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
